/******************************************************************************                      
** Name		 : USP_PP_GetValidationEngineBeneficiaryOnHoldPayment                      
** Short Desc: To get OnHold Payment details
**                      
** Full Description:  To get OnHold Payment details for Beneficiary Payment & PGCalcImport          
**        
**                              
** Input Arguments:
	@UserID INT,
	@Type Bit =1--auto  

**         
** Sample Call     
EXEC USP_PP_GetValidationEngineBeneficiaryOnHoldPayment 1           

                 
